  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a descriptive study to determine the role of fetal GBS disease as a cause for
      stillbirths
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A prospective, descriptive study will be undertaken involving mothers who have a stillbirth
      at Chris Hani Baragwanath Academic Hospital (CHBAH), a secondary-tertiary care hospital, from
      2014 up until 2016.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
